summary: Fenneko x Tsunoda is a ship that could execute the whole “Enemies to lovers” trope right. Neither character has severely hurt...
body: Fenneko x Tsunoda is a ship that could execute the whole “Enemies to lovers” trope right. Neither character has severely hurt the other. It’s mostly just a misunderstanding between them. And really, it’s Fenneko that misjudged Tsunoda, thinking she’s just a kiss-up and all. I think it’d be nice if they bonded and Fenneko has to admit that she was wrong. And maybe once she realizes that Tsunoda is actually pretty smart, then, maybe, some feelings would develop. I strongly doubt this ship will ever be canon but it is nice to think about.

summary:
So here’s a mega collection of @kingdomofkitten’s Ikariverse!
First is when Ikari meets his two friends, Kuuma and Nezumi for...
body:
So here’s a mega collection of @kingdomofkitten’s Ikariverse!

First is when Ikari meets his two friends, Kuuma and Nezumi for the first time.

Next is when he shows his new friends to his dad, building a crib for new sister and his mom, who is pregnant with his new sister.

Third, we have Bezumi getting picked up by he older brother, Haru.

Next up we have Retsuko during her pregnancy, when the sound of chewing gives her a spitting headache. The funny thing is, Doriyakis are actually soft. Last picture is the aftermath of the incident.
